  "texts": [
    "Graph reconstruction models such as MolGrapher, which preserves atom locations, allow the annotator to quickly map the molecular graph with the image, and gain efficiency.",
    "To evaluate the ingestion pipeline, D2C-RND and D2C-UNI are leveraged.",
    "The precision and recall are computed for each ingestion component.",
    "For the segmentation module, a predicted bounding box is considered a true positive if its intersection over union with the ground truth is higher than 95%.",
    "For the classification module, the precision and recall of the predicted 'Molecular Structure' class are computed."
  ],
